    <page name="Priorities" title="Volunteer Prioritization and group interest">
        <html>
            <content>
                <![CDATA[
                    <p>
                        You have chosen to become an active member of a curation group. 
                        
                        In order to best place your efforts, we ask if you would please prioritize your top three curation activites(s) 
                        and expert panel(s) of choice. Further, please indicate any prior experience and willingness to participate in more than one. 
                        
                        Note, you are not obligated to participate in more than one, as each curation effort will have its own training session(s).
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        To learn more about each curation activity see: 
                        <a href="https://www.clinicalgenome.org/curation-activities/">https://www.clinicalgenome.org/curation-activities/</a>. 
                        
                        A description of Somatic Cancer can be found here: 
                        <a href="https://www.clinicalgenome.org/working-groups/somatic/">https://www.clinicalgenome.org/working-groups/somatic/</a>
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        For more information on current expert panels accepting volunteers see: 
                        <a href="https://www.clinicalgenome.org/working-groups/c3/">https://www.clinicalgenome.org/working-groups/c3/</a>
                    </p>
                ]]>
            </content>
        </html>

